@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
title US-08 Test Model (Current Code Reality)

actor Developer
participant "Brain" as BR
participant "ColumnField" as CF

Developer -> BR: step(inputs, learn=False)
activate BR
BR -> BR: encode_only(inputs)
BR -> CF: compute(learn=False)
CF --> BR: inference state
BR --> Developer: decoded outputs / predictions
deactivate BR

note over BR
No dedicated test_model API or RL evaluation
framework is currently implemented.
end note
@enduml
